<item>
            <title>[LANG-487] ToStringBuilder is thread-hostile</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LANG-487</link>
                <project id="12310481" key="LANG">Commons Lang</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ToStringBuilder is thread-hostile due to the use of the static &quot;defaultStyle&quot; variable.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Adding synchronization won&apos;t solve this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12416892">LANG-487</key>
            <summary>ToStringBuilder is thread-hostile</summary>
